Build package form copr dist-git.

    mkdir /tmp/results
    ./copr-builder --copr      praiskup/ping \
                   --package   quick-package \
                   --revision  5ce6ec838e22d \
                   --resultdir /tmp/results


We heavily depend on `rpkg` for working with `dist-git`, and on `copr-cli`
package to obtain mock profile.

Dependencies:
    - copr-cli
    - crudini
    - mock
    - rpkg

(motivation https://bugzilla.redhat.com/show_bug.cgi?id=1410403)
